title: 12/06: Start or Sit (AFC Home Games); Rankings Debates (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Emmanuel Sanders is out (4:00)! What does that mean for Courtland Sutton and the rest of the DEN offense? We've got more news and some rankings debates (9:03) on Deshaun Watson, LeSean McCoy, Philip Rivers and David Njoku. And where is Jaylen Samuels in our TE rankings (17:40)? ... Startometer (24:33) for key players in the NE-MIA and NYJ-BUF game. Do we have faith in Tom Brady this week? And while we preview the 7 games, make sure you listen to our discussion about the uncertainty of the RB position in Week 14 (33:08) and Adam finishing his disgusting Butterfinger at the very end of the show ... PIT-OAK (28:40), BAL-KC (39:00), CIN-LAC (44:00), CAR-CLE (50:25), IND-HOU (57:50), NE-MIA (1:02:50), BUF-NYJ (1:06:25) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
